{
  "name": "Bhai Shamsher Singh (Delhi) – brother of Bhai Santa Singh",
  "url": "https://kirtansewa.net/index.php/bhai-shamsher-singh-delhi-brother-of-bhai-santa-singh/",
  "image_url": "https://cdn.kirtansewa.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/22011618/Bhai-Shamsher-Singhbro-of-Bhai-Santa-Singh.jpg",
  "body": [
    "Bhai Shamsher Singh Ji was the younger brother of renowned puratan Raagi, Bhai Santa Singh Ji. Following the passing of his brother, Bhai Shamsher Singh Ji fronted the jatha and was accompanied by his brothers, Bhai Jabarjang Singh and Bhai Swaran Singh. They traveled to Singapore and were recorded by late Sardar Amir Singh Ji. Most of the recordings below are from their tour to Singapore. Currently, Bhai Swaran Singh Ji’s sons Bhai Harjit Singh, Bhai Gurdeep Singh and Bhai Gurmeet Singh are continuing the family tradition and are serving the Delhi Sikh Gurdwara Committee. If anyone has more recordings of Bhai Shamsher Singh Ji and jatha, please contact us."
